S Based on the findings from the above methods, the interorganizational country team will produce a brief report summarizing any systematic problems with defining indicators and data recording, reporting and aggregation from the facility to the national level (where relevant), data quality challenges, and recommendations to improve the quality of aggregate data reporting and the system that generates the data in the future. This report should be shared with all stakeholders in the interorganizational country team, including implementing partners and Ministries of Health.
